                                                  \b\fs28 CAB BOOKING SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS\par
INTRODUCTION\par
Purpose:\par
\b0\fs24 This system provides customers within the facility with the ability to book cabs smoothly. The customers can modify and are able to cancel the cab for any reason. That prepares within a role and policies. The software should provide an option for checking availability of the cabs. That is important for the customers to get a message if the cab is unavailable. That will be displayed into customers. The customers should be noted when the change has been made or any further changes\b\fs28\par
Intended audience & reading suggection\par
\b0\fs24 This project is a prototype for the cab booking system. This project is useful for the cab management system team and as well as to the passengers.\b\fs28\par
Product scope\par
\b0\fs24 The purpose of the cab booking system is an easy-to-use application for passengers, trying to book online cabs. The system is based on a relational database with its flight management and reservation functions. We will have a database server supporting hundreds of major cities around the world as well as thousands of flights by various airline companies. Above all, we hope to provide a comfortable user experience along with the best pricing available.\b\fs28\par
